                      ],
                      "text": "Stage Introduction",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "\"Meow.\" \"Our senses are very sharp, and when danger approaches, we can practically 'hear' the sound of incoming trouble. As such, all us cats tend to avoid those purplish, square-shaped fellows!\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(204, 191, 173)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Special Rule: \"Electro Hypostasis\" is immune to Frozen, Stun, Petrification and begins with \"Elemental Lifeform: Electro\" attached to it. It will heal until it reaches 6 HP upon triggering \"Electro Crystal Core.\" At the start of the Action Phase: If the Elector Hypostasis does not have \"Electro Crystal Core\" attached, it can reapply \"Electro Crystal Core.\" (This effect can be triggered twice at most.)",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
